{"id":2007,"title":"[Clinical analysis on combined medication in patients of acute pancreatitis in real world].","abstract":"To study the characteristics and regular pattern of the medicine in common use and combined medication in patients of acute pancreatitis in real world.Collect the information of 5 433 acute pancreatitis patients in 19 grade IIIA general hospitals in China, analysis by descriptive statistics and association rule.In the 5 433 patients of acute pancreatitis, the glycyrrhizic acid injection and somatostatin are the frequency top used Chinese traditional and western medication. Glycyrrhizic acid injection, somatostatin and insulin are the frequency top used drug combination pattern.The Chinese and western integrative medicine drug use pattern are accord with the clinical guideline of acute panceatitis. The hepatic and renal function, blood routine and coagulation function should be monitored when the medicines are used.","date":"2014-12-23","categories":"Digestive System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25532389","annotations":[{"name":"Insulin","weight":0.798641,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Insulin"},{"name":"Alternative medicine","weight":0.797336,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alternative_medicine"},{"name":"Coagulation","weight":0.791023,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coagulation"},{"name":"Medical guideline","weight":0.780388,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_guideline"},{"name":"Renal function","weight":0.772901,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Renal_function"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.75303,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Pharmaceutical drug","weight":0.717419,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pharmaceutical_drug"},{"name":"Liver","weight":0.71741,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liver"},{"name":"Blood","weight":0.691549,"wikipedia_ar